snippet.title: Party Animals - Official Console Announce Trailer - Xbox & Bethesda Games Showcase 2021
snippet.description:
Get ready to party like an animal. Party Animals is coming to Xbox Game Pass in 2022.
https://www.xbox.com/games/party-animals

Fight with or against your friends in Party Animals! Choose your character from a diverse cast of adorable animals as you battle it out across multiple game modes to be the last one left standing in the ultimate competitive brawler.

Subscribe to Xbox 🎮  https://xbx.lv/2EEjmaR 

Follow Xbox on other channels: 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Xbox
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/Xbox
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/Xbox

AUDIO DESCRIPTION: https://youtu.be/xgLh_AW1kYs
